"exporter" means any person, firm or company carrying on
    the business of exporting from the Island specially
    protected produce;
"fruit" means bananas and citrus fruit and any fruit which
      the Minister may declare to be fruit for the purposes of
      this Act;
"inspected" means inspected under the provisions of this
     Act;
"Inspector" means Inspector of Agricultural Produce;
"licensed vehicle" means a vehicle in respect of which a
     licence is granted under section 17;
"nutmegs" means nutmegs, whether in the pod or separated
    from the pod, whether cured or uncured, ripe or
    unripe, and mace;
